videos.headline: Vermont's Davis grabs the and-1 bucket
videos.description: Ryan Davis gets the and-1 bucket to fall as Vermont leads UMBC.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Vermont's Davis grabs the and-1 bucket) 2022/03/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Powell grabs a bucket for Vermont
videos.description: Isaiah Powell makes a great effort inside to grab the Catamounts' bucket.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Powell grabs a bucket for Vermont) 2022/03/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Vermont's Duncan gets the score inside
videos.description: Robin Duncan makes a great move to get to the basket as Vermont continues to roll vs. UMBC.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Vermont's Duncan gets the score inside) 2022/03/12 ESHEET

videos.headline: Shungu throws down slam for Vermont
videos.description: Ben Shungu throws down the dunk for Vermont as they continue to pad their lead vs. UMBC.

videos.headline: Vermont's Deloney knocks down 3-pointer
videos.description: Aaron Deloney gets the 3-pointer to fall for the Catamounts.

videos.headline: Vermont defeats UMBC to clinch tournament berth
videos.description: Vermont clinches the tournament berth as they take care of UMBC, 82-43.
